lead_paragraph: Infielder Pedro Alvarez and the Baltimore Orioles have agreed to a $5.75 million, one-year contract, a person familiar with the negotiations said Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: AP Source: Alvarez, Orioles Agree to $5.75M, 1-Year Deal
